targets.query: SELECT distinct("value") /1000000000 FROM "upstream_rx" WHERE ("host" = 'service_group_0' AND "type" = 'bits_per_second') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT sum("last") / 1000000000
FROM
(
SELECT last("value") 
FROM "autogen"."upstream_rx" 
WHERE ( "type" = 'bits_per_second')
GROUP BY host
)

SELECT sum("last") / 1000000000
FROM
(
SELECT last("value") 
FROM "autogen"."upstream_tx" 
WHERE ( "type" = 'bits_per_second')
GROUP BY host
)
